<text corresp="#SS"><body>
  <milestone n="503" unit="page" facs="631"/>
  <head><lb n="26"/>pāṭṭu – 400 : talaivaṉ cuṟṟu</head>
    <p xml:id="KT400-kilavi">
    <lb n="27"/>tuṟai :― viṉaimuṟṟi vanta talaivaṉ tērppākaṉait talai<lb n="28"/>yaḷittatu.
  </p>
   
  <milestone n="504" unit="page" facs="632"/>
  <lg xml:id="KT400">
    <l><lb n="3"/>400. cēyāṟu celvā māyiṉ· iṭariṉṟu</l>
    <l><lb n="4"/>kaḷaikalam kāmam peruntōṭ keṉṟu</l>
    <l><lb n="5"/>naṉṟupurin teṇṇiya maṉattai yāki</l>
    <l><lb n="6"/>murampukaṇ uṭaiya vēkik karampaip</l>
    <l><lb n="7"/>putuvaḻip paṭutta matiyuṭai valavōy</l>
    <l><lb n="8"/>iṉṟu tantaṉai tērō</l>
    <l><lb n="9"/>nōyuḻan tuṟaiviyai nalka lāṉē.</l>
  </lg>
  <p>
    ―pēyaṉār.
  </p>
